<h5 lang="en" id="calibre_link-1">Introductory provisions</h5>
<p lang="en">SHOPSOFT, (hereinafter "Verse Surf", “we” or “us”) is a company that treats all the matters related to personal data with utter respect and integrity. Our full commitment to safeguarding your privacy, and the privacy of our platform and Game, represents a particularly high priority for our company. </p>
