<h5 id="calibre_link-17" lang="en">Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h5>
<p lang="en"><span>We use cookies technologies in order to improve your experience while visiting our platform and Game.  Wherever the case, we use a cookie control system (Cookie Popup Message) allowing you on your first visit to the platform and Game to permit or block the use of certain cookies categories on your device. This Cookie Popup Message complies with all the recent legislation updated requirements in order to obtain explicit consent.</span></p>
